00:40:12,360 --> 00:40:14,360
Tadi kubilang kamu luar biasa.

972
00:40:14,600 --> 00:40:15,520
Dipahami?

973
00:40:15,840 --> 00:40:16,680
Guru, dengarkan.

974
00:40:16,680 --> 00:40:17,840
Meskipun kamu mentraktirku minum hari ini,

975
00:40:18,080 --> 00:40:19,920
