976
00:40:20,080 --> 00:40:21,080
Kami membutuhkan lebih banyak.

977
00:40:21,840 --> 00:40:24,480
Menurut Ringkasan Materia Medica,

978
00:40:24,480 --> 00:40:25,520
mengonsumsi alkohol secara berlebihan

979
00:40:25,880 --> 00:40:27,880
