992
00:40:51,080 --> 00:40:51,920
Baiklah.

993
00:40:52,040 --> 00:40:53,240
Mulutmu berminyak sekali.

994
00:40:53,240 --> 00:40:54,320
Bersihkan mulutmu.

995
00:40:54,520 --> 00:40:55,840
Berhenti minum.

996
00:40:58,000 --> 00:40:59,400
